# Add Parent-Facing Frontend Sections

This adds several new frontend-only pages and enhances existing ones for the **parent** (and student) roles. All data uses the existing mock data system — no backend needed.

## Proposed Changes

---

### Mock Data Layer

#### [MODIFY] [mockData.ts](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/lib/mockData.ts)
- Add `mockTestResults` — richer marks data with school test & tuition test distinction, grade, percentage, and term
- Add `mockWeeklyAttendance` — daily attendance for current week per student
- Add `mockMonthlyAttendance` — per-month summary (days present, absent, %, month name)
- Add `mockAbsenceNotifications` — list of absence-alert notifications
- Add `mockNotes` extended — notes with `type` (`handwritten` | `video` | `ppt`), subject, thumbnail/url
- Add `mockBatchAchievements` — previous batch toppers with name, year, percentage, rank, college
- Extend [resolveMock()](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/lib/mockData.ts#227-278) to serve new API paths

---

### New Pages

#### [NEW] [ParentTestResults.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/pages/ParentTestResults.tsx)
- Parent/student read-only view of school test & tuition test marks
- Tabs: School Tests | Tuition Tests
- Table with: Test name, Subject, Marks, Total, %, Grade, Date, Remarks
- Colour-coded grade badges (A+/A/B/C/F)
- Filter dropdown by subject

#### [NEW] [Achievements.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/pages/Achievements.tsx)
- Previous batch results/toppers hall of fame
- Cards for Gold🥇/Silver🥈/Bronze🥉 toppers
- Table for all achievers: Name, Batch Year, %, College Admitted
- Prominent header with institute branding

---

### Modified Pages

#### [MODIFY] [Attendance.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/pages/Attendance.tsx)
- When `role === "parent"` or `"student"`:
  - Show **weekly calendar view** (Mon-Sat grid for current week)
  - Show **monthly summary** (% present + bar chart using CSS)
  - Show **Absence Alert panel** — red alert card listing absent dates with "Notification Sent" badge

#### [MODIFY] [Notes.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/pages/Notes.tsx)
- Add **subject tabs** (Mathematics, Science, English)
- Add **type filter chips**: All | 📝 Handwritten | 🎥 Video | 📊 PPT
- Note cards show type icon, date, teacher name
- Make Notes accessible to `parent` role in sidebar

---

### Routing & Navigation

#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/App.tsx)
- Add routes: `/test-results`, `/achievements`

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/components/Sidebar.tsx)
- Add "Test Results" nav item for `parent`, `student`
- Add "Achievements" nav item for all roles
- Add "Study Notes" for `parent` role (currently excluded)
- Add `NotificationBell` in sidebar footer for `parent`

#### [NEW] [NotificationBell.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Prashik%20Pawar/Downloads/Attached-Assets/Attached-Assets/client/src/components/NotificationBell.tsx)
- Bell icon with red badge for unread absence notifications
- Popover dropdown listing unread absent alerts

